data.description: ADORABLE CAPE COD on CORNER LOT in Historic Leonardtown, MD! This 4 Bed, 2.5 Bath home features a 1-Car Detached Shed/Workshop/Garage, Paved Driveway, Architectural Shingles, Fenced-in Back Yard, Deck, Main Floor Primary Bedroom w/ walk-in closet along with Primary Bathroom, Laundry on Upper Level, Beautiful Updated Kitchen w/ Pantry, SS Appliances, Dining Area, Combination Dining & Livingroom, Tub/Shower Combinations, and Built-ins, NO HOA! This home is located in the St. Clements Shores Water Oriented Community and offers access to the community beach, pier and pavilion as well as access to the community boat ramp with an optional and minimal annual community recreation paid fee. Enjoy the convenience of being close to the Water, Golf Course/Country Club, Nightlife, Grocery Stores, Shopping, Boutique Shops, Gas Stations, Banks, Hospital, Restaurants, Post Office, Downtown Leonardtown, Leonardtown Wharf, College, Parks, Winery, and SO MUCH MORE! Come fall in love with The Woods at Bayside and live your HAPPILY EVER AFTER!
